name: Rabbit Delirium #2
description:
I created the Schizoid Bunny, but not the Rabbit Delirium. They are just hallucinations of the Schizoid Bunny, they are in their imagination.
If you have purchased 5 or more bunny editions, you will receive this Rabbit Delirium.
If you are an anonymous collector and agree to have me send it to you, please contact me somehow so I know.
